              "subject": "[PATCH] userfaultfd: wait on source PMD during UFFDIO_MOVE",
              "date": "2026-07-05T13:12:44Z"
            }
          ],
          "series_items": [],
          "patch_summary": "This patch fixes a bug in the userfaultfd code where it incorrectly passes a pointer to src_pmdval instead of the actual PMD (page-table entry) when calling pmd_migration_entry_wait(). The fix involves passing the correct PMD, src_pmd, which matches the behavior in other parts of the kernel. This change ensures that the wait operation is properly synchronized with the real page-table lock, preventing potential issues on split-PMD-lock kernels.",
